org.svvrl.goal.core.io
Class GFFCodec

java.lang.Object
  org.svvrl.goal.core.io.XMLCodec
      org.svvrl.goal.core.io.GFFCodec
All Implemented Interfaces:
Codec
public class GFFCodec
extends XMLCodec

A GFFCodec is an XML codec with the ability to encode/decode automata and logic formulae. This codec is composed by QPTLCodec, FSACodec, TwoWayAltAutomatonCodec, AltAutomatonCodec, and GameCodec. The default file extension is ".gff".

Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
